大隻曾經被一向撐開佢既契仔鄭俊弘 (宜家改左名叫鄭欣宜)同其他會員篤爆佢係肥佬扮女人:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s10.postimg.org/eq8erqgi1/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs10.postimg.org%2Feq8erqgi1%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png&h=99e1c7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/mhshwom03/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fmhshwom03%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png&h=2dcd081b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續去死撐啦，同快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679830b0df74bc7d462623d1bf9acc027f511732","tid":530724,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>陰功得過你條傻鳩大隻? 睇下你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/2hx06o3i3j/1507948730452.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F2hx06o3i3j%2F1507948730452.png&h=24ca1f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正常男人望下面就望到自己賓周，但你睇下自己幾撚大個肚腩，本癲狗好心，建議下你照鏡等自己睇到粒賓周仔，點知原來你條傻鳩唔識中文衝出黎柒:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/324dmgopy7/Screenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F324dmgopy7%2FScreenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png&h=a28273a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>肥鳩大隻連解讀中文&ldquo;你照鏡咪知囉懵撚&rdquo;哩句句子都有困難，自己柒左仲要周圍話俾人知，不如學好d中文先出黎教人啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></span></span>"},{"pid":"d